dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography and places of historical interest; imaginary view of the destruction of Jericho.
At head of title: Quarta etas mundi -- Folium L.
Descriptive text throughout: Jericho olim regalis...
Appears in Liber cronicarum ... Augsburg, Johann Schoensberger, 1496. A pirated editon of Schedel's Liber cronicarum. Nuernberg, 1493.
